unittitle_ssm: Richard Evelyn Byrd honorary reception materials
abstract_ssm: This collection contains materials relating to a reception held at Brooklyn's Hotel St. George in 1930 to honor Rear Admiral Richard Evelyn Byrd. Items include a reception program, a seating arrangement chart, and a photogravure portrait of Byrd.
